<p>Chapel Studios may collect statistics about the behavior of visitors to its website. Chapel Studios may display this information publicly or provide it to others. However, Chapel Studios does not disclose your personally-identifying information.</p>


<h2>Cookies</h2>
<p>To enrich and perfect your online experience, Chapel Studios uses "Cookies", similar technologies and services provided by others to display personalized content, appropriate advertising and store your preferences on your computer.</p>
<p>A cookie is a string of information that a website stores on a visitor's computer, and that the visitor's browser provides to the website each time the visitor returns. Chapel Studios uses cookies to help Chapel Studios identify and track visitors, their usage of https://www.ChapelStudios.dev, and their website access preferences. Chapel Studios visitors who do not wish to have cookies placed on their computers should set their browsers to refuse cookies before using Chapel Studios's websites, with the drawback that certain features of Chapel Studios's websites may not function properly without the aid of cookies.</p>
<p>By continuing to navigate our website without changing your cookie settings, you hereby acknowledge and agree to Chapel Studios's use of cookies.</p>



